"Peeta. Peeta, wake up," I say in a soft, singsong voice.His eyelids flutter open and then he jumps like we''ve stabbed him. "Aa!"Finnick and I fall back in the sand, laughing our heads off. Every time we try to stop, we look at Peeta''s attempt to maintain a disdainful expression and it sets us off again.', 18, 0), (7947, 'I love books, by the way, way more than movies. Movies tell you what to think. A good book lets you choose a few thoughts for yourself. Movies show you the pink house. A good book tells you there''s a pink house and lets you paint some of the finishing touches, maybe choose the roof style,park your own car out front. My imagination has always topped anything a movie could come up with. Case in point, those darned Harry Potter movies. That was so not what that part-Veela-chick, Fleur Delacour, looked like.', 118, 0), (7948, 'If you want to know what God thinks of money, just look at the people he gave it to.', 201, 0), (7949, 'Confidence is ignorance. If you''re feeling cocky, it''s because there''s something you don''t know.', 958, 0), (7950, 'Jace shook his blond head in exasperation. "You had to make a crazy jail friend, didn''t you? You couldn''t just count ceiling tiles or tame a pet mouse like normal prisoners do?', 39, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (7951, 'Animals are my friends...and I don''t eat my friends.', 266, 0), (7952, 'A smile is a curve that sets everything straight.', 2181, 0), (7953, 'In the beginning there was nothing, which exploded.', 195, 0), (7954, 'The longer and more carefully we look at a funny story, the sadder it becomes.', 1075, 0), (7955, 'My rapier wit hides my inner pain.', 39, 0), (7956, 'Headline?" he asked."''Swing Set Needs Home,''" I said."''Desperately Lonely Swing Set Needs Loving Home,''" he said."''Lonely, Vaguely Pedophilic Swing Set Seeks the Butts of Children,''" I said.', 9, 0), (7957, 'I always arrive late at the office, but I make up for it by leaving early.', 2182, 0), (7958, 'I have the simplest tastes. I am always satisfied with the best.', 40, 0), (7959, 'Black holes are where God divided by zero.', 104, 0), (7960, 'There is only one thing in the world worse than being talked about, and that is not being talked about.', 40, 0), (7961, 'Some people have a way with words, and other people...oh, uh, not have way.', 748, 0), (7962, 'Forgive, O Lord, my little jokes on TheeAnd I''ll forgive Thy great big one on me.', 35, 0), (7963, 'Magnus, standing by the door, snapped his fingers impatiently. "Move it along, teenagers. The only person who gets to canoodle in my bedroom is my magnificent self.""Canoodle?" repeated Clary, never having heard the word before."Magnificent?" repeated Jace, who was just being nasty. Magnus growled. The growl sounded like "Get out.', 39, 0), (7964, 'Ginny!" said Mr. Weasley, flabbergasted. "Haven''t I taught you anything? What have I always told you? Never trust anything that can think for itself if you can''t see where it keeps its brain?', 28, 0), (7965, 'Why are you worrying about YOU-KNOW-WHO, when you should be worrying about YOU-NO-POO? The constipation sensation that''s gripping the nation!', 28, 0), (7966, 'An Unbreakable Vow?" said Ron, looking stunned. "Nah, he can’t have.... 